WARNING:

This version of the port is incompatible with the previous ones, so
please make sure you don't have any 
  export CC=/usr/bin/distcc-gcc 
or 
  export CXX=/usr/bin/distcc-g++
in your startup/configuration files; this will make compilations fail.


POST-INSTALL
to use distcc, just 
a) export DISTCC_HOSTS to include the compilation hosts
b) prepend /usr/lib/distcc to your $PATH environment variable.
   (e.g. in pkgmk.conf)
c) export MAKEFLAGS=-j<n> where n is a number representing the number of
   parallel jobs you want
